General.Name: Sacgasco Ltd
General.Description: Sacgasco Limited engages in oil and gas exploration, development, and production activities. It holds interests in a suite of assets located in the Sacramento Basin of California, as well as Canada and the Philippines. The company was formerly known as Australian Oil Company Limited and changed its name to Sacgasco Limited in November 2015. Sacgasco Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Subiaco, Australia.
